title: AMAZING CORNER UNIT IN ICON BAY!!
posting_body: ['Fantastic 2 bedrooms +den, two baths condo at Icon Bay with amazing Bay and City views!!', 'Great building with Resort style amenities, infinity pool, 2 tennis courts, Gym, Spa, Party room, theater, and pool table.', 'Decorated with an excellent taste and fully equipped.', 'One King size bed and Queen bed in the second bedroom Edgewater neighborhood offers superb restaurants, and shops, nightlife, close to the airport', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
